# ACD Call Understanding

_Living document — updated as I learn more_

## Call Structure

| Call | Focus | Frequency | Day | Time |
|------|-------|-----------|-----|------|
| **ACDE** | Execution Layer | Bi-weekly | Thursday | 14:00 UTC |
| **ACDC** | Consensus Layer | Bi-weekly | Thursday | 14:00 UTC |
| **ACDT** | Testing/Implementation | Weekly | Monday | 14:00 UTC |

ACDE and ACDC alternate Thursdays. ACDT happens every Monday.

